About
=====

A parser for the Promela modeling language.
`PLY <https://pypi.python.org/pypi/ply/3.4>`__ (Python ``lex``-``yacc``)
is used to generate the parser. Classes for a Promela abstract tree are
included and used for representing the result of parsing. A short
tutorial can be found in the file ``doc.md``. To install:

::

    pip install promela
